EN: They decided to increase the number of production lines.

ZH: 我们需要增加员工的数量来完成这个项目。
EN: We need to increase the number of staff to complete this project.

ZH: 最近天气变得寒冷，我们应该增加衣服的厚度。
EN: The weather has become cold recently. We should increase the thickness of our clothes.

